WEBVTT

21:16.000 --> 21:18.390 line:80%
Your Majesty, I implore you

21:18.590 --> 21:21.200 line:80%
to revoke the restoration order
for the front line.

21:21.200 --> 21:23.710 line:80%
I humbly ask for Your Majesty's judgment.

21:24.200 --> 21:27.420 line:80%
The situation on the front line
changes rapidly.
